11:48.791 --> 11:50.001
I need a good big brother

11:50.043 --> 11:51.586
before it's too late!

11:51.628 --> 11:53.754
I'm like one wedgie away

11:51.628 --> 11:53.754
from an eating disorder.

11:53.796 --> 11:55.549
You're here by yourself?

11:55.590 --> 11:58.009
Francis, please, all

11:55.590 --> 11:58.009
I want is a few minutes

11:58.051 --> 11:59.760
of someone being nice to me.

