I have the day off Saturday.

12:10.855 --> 12:11.981
I'll bring him home then.

12:12.023 --> 12:14.025
You gotta give him

12:12.023 --> 12:14.025
credit, you know.

12:14.067 --> 12:15.985
He got to the ranch

12:14.067 --> 12:15.985
all by himself.

12:16.027 --> 12:18.572
The first time you tried,

12:16.027 --> 12:18.572
you ended up in Mexico.

12:18.613 --> 12:19.573
Of course, I'd be happy

12:19.614 --> 12:20.781
to carry your bags outside.

12:20.823 --> 12:21.782
We wouldn't want you

12:21.824 --> 12:23.368
to get all hot and sweaty

12:23.410 --> 12:25.370
out in the blaring heat

12:23.410 --> 12:25.370
of the parking lot.

12:25.412 --> 12:28.164
Malcolm. You're not

12:25.412 --> 12:28.164
scheduled for today.

12:28.206 --> 12:29.457
I'm just looking

12:28.206 --> 12:29.457
for my mom.

12:29.499 --> 12:31.209
She's out back on her break.

12:33.628 --> 12:34.962
Last night, Mom accused me

12:35.004 --> 12:37.424
of being obsessive

12:35.004 --> 12:37.424
about getting written up.

12:37.465 --> 12:38.799
So I stayed up all last night

12:38.841 --> 12:39.967
thinking up

12:38.841 --> 12:39.967
a bunch of comebacks,

12:40.009 --> 12:41.595
and I even have

12:40.009 --> 12:41.595
potential comebacks

12:41.636 --> 12:43.804
to every possible comeback

12:41.636 --> 12:43.804
of hers. There is no way she...

12:43.846 --> 12:45.265
(gasps)

12:56.150 --> 12:57.110
You're smoking?!

12:57.151 --> 12:58.986
After all the times

12:57.151 --> 12:58.986
you lectured us?

12:59.028 --> 13:00.196
After telling us

12:59.028 --> 13:00.196
if we smoked,

13:00.238 --> 13:02.073
you would kill us

13:00.238 --> 13:02.073
before the cancer did?!

13:02.115 --> 13:03.032
After you would

13:02.115 --> 13:03.032
push Francis'

13:03.074 --> 13:05.076
lit cigarettes back in his mouth

13:05.118 --> 13:07.662
and make him swallow?!

13:05.118 --> 13:07.662
And you smoke?!

13:08.455 --> 13:09.664
You smoke?!

13:10.665 --> 13:12.626
Look, it's not what you think.

13:12.667 --> 13:13.627
When I work,

13:13.668 --> 13:14.628
I have two cigarettes--

13:14.669 --> 13:16.463
one on my morning break,

13:14.669 --> 13:16.463
one in the afternoon.

13:16.504 --> 13:17.464
No more, no less.

13:17.505 --> 13:18.839
Who are you?!

13:18.881 --> 13:20.634
You have to stop saying that.

13:20.675 --> 13:21.635
I will quit eventually,

13:21.676 --> 13:23.428
but until then, the only thing

13:23.470 --> 13:25.012
that's stopping your father

13:25.054 --> 13:26.847
from smoking six packs a day

13:26.889 --> 13:28.849
is knowing that

13:26.889 --> 13:28.849
we quit together.

13:28.891 --> 13:29.850
But you didn't quit.

13:29.892 --> 13:31.852
But he knows I did.

13:31.894 --> 13:32.853
But you didn't!

13:32.895 --> 13:35.231
He knows I did.

13:35.273 --> 13:37.651
You lie and you smoke.

13:37.692 --> 13:39.653
Oh, for God's sake, Malcolm.

13:39.694 --> 13:40.861
Lois, Lois, I just remembered

13:40.903 --> 13:43.281
you were holding

13:40.903 --> 13:43.281
my lit cigarette in your hand,

13:43.323 --> 13:44.324
and I wanted

13:43.323 --> 13:44.324
to thank you

13:44.365 --> 13:46.033
for holding on

13:44.365 --> 13:46.033
to my cigarettes...

13:46.075 --> 13:47.034
which are mine.

13:47.076 --> 13:48.869
He knows.

13:47.076 --> 13:48.869
Okay.

13:48.911 --> 13:52.457
I think I left

13:48.911 --> 13:52.457
my register open.

13:52.499 --> 13:54.875
Okay, Malcolm, you caught me.

13:55.918 --> 13:57.671
This has to be kept secret.

13:57.712 --> 13:59.880
So I'm going to ask you

13:57.712 --> 13:59.880
for a favor.

13:59.922 --> 14:01.508
A favor?

14:01.549 --> 14:02.883
You're asking me

14:01.549 --> 14:02.883
for a favor

14:02.925 --> 14:04.469
after you totally

14:02.925 --> 14:04.469
hung me out to dry.

14:04.511 --> 14:06.053
I'm just asking for

14:04.511 --> 14:06.053
a little flexibility.

14:06.095 --> 14:07.472
Please.

14:07.514 --> 14:08.889
For your father and for me,

14:08.931 --> 14:11.100
just keep the smoking

14:08.931 --> 14:11.100
to yourself.

14:11.142 --> 14:12.352
Please.

14:13.812 --> 14:15.772
Yeah, okay.

14:15.814 --> 14:17.940
Wow, she's talking to me

14:15.814 --> 14:17.940
like a human being.

14:17.982 --> 14:19.567
This can't get

14:17.982 --> 14:19.567
any weirder.

14:19.609 --> 14:22.069
Thank you, Malcolm.

14:22.111 --> 14:24.531
Yes, it can.

14:24.572 --> 14:25.906
I can't believe

14:24.572 --> 14:25.906
I used to think

14:25.948 --> 14:27.908
that taking care

14:25.948 --> 14:27.908
of the baby was a chore.

14:27.950 --> 14:29.869
This class has

14:27.950 --> 14:29.869
really opened my eyes.

14:32.955 --> 14:34.165
Time.

14:36.751 --> 14:37.918
Aiden wins again.

14:37.960 --> 14:42.131
I knew I shouldn't let you have

14:37.960 --> 14:42.131
that cracker.

14:42.173 --> 14:43.299
I'll pay you

14:42.173 --> 14:43.299
next class.

14:43.341 --> 14:44.509
I got to go.

14:44.551 --> 14:45.510
You're not going

14:44.551 --> 14:45.510
to stick around

14:45.552 --> 14:47.178
for the suction contest?

14:48.179 --> 14:49.930
Will you take a watch?

14:49.972 --> 14:52.350
Don't get too down about

14:49.972 --> 14:52.350
this probation thing.

14:52.392 --> 14:54.935
This job is mostly

14:52.392 --> 14:54.935
a beauty pageant.

14:54.977 --> 14:56.312
You know what's weird?

14:56.354 --> 14:59.106
You get used to thinking

14:56.354 --> 14:59.106
of a person as being

14:59.148 --> 15:00.941
so much more powerful

14:59.148 --> 15:00.941
than you,

15:00.983 --> 15:03.944
then something shifts and

15:00.983 --> 15:03.944
it becomes kind of awkward.

15:03.986 --> 15:06.113
Oh, my God, are you

15:03.986 --> 15:06.113
my boss now?!

15:03.986 --> 15:06.113
What?

15:06.155 --> 15:07.114
This is so unfair.

15:07.156 --> 15:08.115
Year after year,

15:08.157 --> 15:10.951
why can't...

15:10.993 --> 15:13.120
It's nice to see one

15:10.993 --> 15:13.120
of the good guys win.

15:13.162 --> 15:14.955
Why don't you

15:13.162 --> 15:14.955
take a load off.

15:14.997 --> 15:16.332
I'll go get you

15:14.997 --> 15:16.332
a cup of joe.

15:16.374 --> 15:17.667
No worries, chief.

15:23.381 --> 15:25.174
(grunting)

15:35.643 --> 15:37.061
Whoa.

15:42.191 --> 15:43.610
Malcolm.

15:45.486 --> 15:47.154
It's not what it looks like.

15:47.196 --> 15:48.782
YOUNG:

15:47.196 --> 15:48.782
Lois, sorry,

15:47.196 --> 15:48.782
are you in there?

15:48.823 --> 15:49.783
I'll explain later.

15:49.824 --> 15:51.451
I know exactly what this

15:49.824 --> 15:51.451
looks like to you,

15:51.492 --> 15:53.244
but I'm asking you for

15:51.492 --> 15:53.244
a little flexibility.

15:53.286 --> 15:54.245
Trust me.

15:54.287 --> 15:55.371
Lois, where's the...?

15:55.413 --> 15:57.373
What's going on here?

15:57.415 --> 15:59.459
Well, I'll have to

15:57.415 --> 15:59.459
