He's flattened

16:00.627 --> 16:01.586
another box

16:01.628 --> 16:03.087
outside of the box

16:01.628 --> 16:03.087
flattening area.

16:09.051 --> 16:11.011
The guys at work are great.

16:11.053 --> 16:13.598
I already have a nickname--

16:11.053 --> 16:13.598
Ten Fingers.

16:13.640 --> 16:16.016
The old Ten Fingers

16:13.640 --> 16:16.016
wasn't using it anymore.

16:16.058 --> 16:17.477
I'm proud of you, son.

16:17.518 --> 16:19.019
You're working now.

16:19.061 --> 16:22.064
I feel like I could

16:19.061 --> 16:22.064
talk to you, man to man.

16:22.106 --> 16:24.275
You know, about

16:22.106 --> 16:24.275
grown up things--

16:24.317 --> 16:25.860
expenses...

16:25.902 --> 16:27.027
cheaters...

16:27.069 --> 16:29.029
Can I borrow

16:27.069 --> 16:29.029
