16:29.071 --> 16:30.907
Yeah. How much do you need?

16:30.949 --> 16:34.661
Uh... how much do you have?

16:36.454 --> 16:39.457
Why don't you just tell me

16:36.454 --> 16:39.457
how much you need.

16:41.250 --> 16:43.252
100... 2...

16:44.462 --> 16:45.880
and another 100.

16:47.089 --> 16:50.050
You might want to rinse off

16:47.089 --> 16:50.050
