18:21.183 --> 18:22.309
Anyway, you're off probation.

18:22.351 --> 18:24.520
Wow, thanks for going

18:22.351 --> 18:24.520
to the mat for me.

18:24.562 --> 18:25.772
What is your problem?

18:25.813 --> 18:28.608
My problem is, I have

18:25.813 --> 18:28.608
no idea who you are.

18:28.649 --> 18:30.150
I thought I had

18:28.649 --> 18:30.150
this mother

18:30.192 --> 18:32.570
that was abrupt

18:30.192 --> 18:32.570
and short-tempered and rude,

18:32.612 --> 18:35.406
but who at least would stand up

18:32.612 --> 18:35.406
for what's right.

18:35.448 --> 18:36.950
That's not who you are.

18:36.991 --> 18:38.534
I did something nice for you,

18:38.576 --> 18:39.744
and you act like it

18:38.576 --> 18:39.744
didn't even happen.

18:39.786 --> 18:41.161
You did something nice for me

18:41.203 --> 18:42.747
because it was

18:41.203 --> 18:42.747
the right thing to do.

18:42.789 --> 18:45.332
I'm simply making you obey rules

18:42.789 --> 18:45.332
because I'm your mother.

18:45.374 --> 18:47.043
That's not fair.

18:47.085 --> 18:48.419
If this favor thing

18:47.085 --> 18:48.419
doesn't work both ways,

18:48.461 --> 18:50.337
then why am I keeping

18:48.461 --> 18:50.337
a big secret for you?

18:50.379 --> 18:52.172
Why shouldn't I just tell Dad?

18:52.214 --> 18:53.173
You're not going

18:52.214 --> 18:53.173
to tell your father.

18:53.215 --> 18:54.341
How do you know?

18:54.383 --> 18:57.177
Because, Malcolm,

18:54.383 --> 18:57.177
that's not who you are.

18:59.806 --> 19:01.181
Why do you do this to me?

19:01.223 --> 19:03.559
Malcolm, I know

19:01.223 --> 19:03.559
this is hard for you.

19:03.601 --> 19:04.978
You're growing up.

19:05.019 --> 19:06.186
You're sick of living

19:05.019 --> 19:06.186
under my authority.

19:06.228 --> 19:07.772
You want me to cut

19:06.228 --> 19:07.772
you some slack.

19:07.814 --> 19:08.773
You're wondering

19:07.814 --> 19:08.773
when I'll finally

19:08.815 --> 19:11.442
see you as an adult.

19:11.484 --> 19:13.360
Well... that's never

19:11.484 --> 19:13.360
going to happen.

19:13.402 --> 19:14.821
That's just not

19:13.402 --> 19:14.821
the way

19:14.862 --> 19:15.863
it works.

19:15.905 --> 19:18.198
You can move

19:15.905 --> 19:18.198
away from home,

19:18.240 --> 19:20.200
you can get married,

19:18.240 --> 19:20.200
even have kids of your own,

19:20.242 --> 19:23.579
you can even become

19:20.242 --> 19:23.579
a professor of physics at MIT.

19:23.621 --> 19:25.623
I will always be your mother.

19:25.665 --> 19:29.168
And that's just the way

19:25.665 --> 19:29.168
it is until one of us dies.

19:30.419 --> 19:31.378
You want to put your head

19:31.420 --> 19:33.047
between your knees

19:31.420 --> 19:33.047
for a few seconds?

19:33.089 --> 19:34.841
No, I'm okay.

19:35.633 --> 19:36.592
Look...

19:36.634 --> 19:37.635
will you please

19:37.677 --> 19:39.219
just give me one thing?

19:40.262 --> 19:41.806
Please stop smoking.

19:41.848 --> 19:43.182
I already quit.

19:44.266 --> 19:46.102
Are you lying?

19:46.144 --> 19:48.062
Of course not.

20:01.492 --> 20:02.618
Okay, Jamie.

20:02.660 --> 20:04.244
It all comes down to this.

20:04.286 --> 20:06.873
Just do it like we practiced

20:04.286 --> 20:06.873
in the garage.

20:20.678 --> 20:22.262
Go, go, go.

20:22.304 --> 20:23.681
We've got the whole family

20:22.304 --> 20:23.681
together.

20:23.723 --> 20:25.683
We should celebrate with

20:23.723 --> 20:25.683
a nice dinner at...

20:25.725 --> 20:28.227
(Hal murmuring)

20:30.897 --> 20:32.314
(cheering)

20:35.693 --> 20:37.277
Pay up, suckers!

20:37.319 --> 20:39.446
You treated your babies

20:39.488 --> 20:41.532
like they were made of glass,

20:41.574 --> 20:43.076
and now you suffer.

20:43.117 --> 20:44.284
(Hal cackling)

20:44.326 --> 20:45.661
What are you waiting for?

20:45.703 --> 20:48.330
I want to remember

20:45.703 --> 20:48.330
that goofy smile.

20:48.372 --> 20:51.876
Nobody's going to be

20:48.372 --> 20:51.876
seeing that for a long time.

20:51.918 --> 20:54.003
Whoo-hoo! Whoo-hoo!

20:51.918 --> 20:54.003
Look at me! Whoo-hoo!
